    <h1>Knowledge Panel</h1>
    <p class="description">The structured information box Google displays for recognized entities — businesses, people, and brands. A verified knowledge panel <strong>boosts branded CTR by ~30%</strong> and signals that Google understands your business well enough to describe it.</p>
